{"tid":2406171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"My Little Airport:  那陣時不知道 置身的日子都發亮 眼光裡藏著的囂張 往後已不再同樣","createTime":"2021-02-13T03:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T08:57:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4e8c77614f795ad7fe4fc2cfd65f7cfab1b6c95","tid":2406171,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5xi49OreS3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5xi49OreS3k&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=812d01e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5xi49OreS3k</a><br />\n<br />\n如像九十年代初<br />\n照片裡海灘的印象<br />\n那種下午沒有重量<br />\n帶點迷惘奔向夕陽<br />\n<br />\n那年獨自去南洋<br />\n一杯白咖啡的早上<br />\n四周是可冒險方向<br />\n尤加利樹葉的香<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n置身的日子都發亮<br />\n眼光裡藏著的囂張<br />\n往後已不再同樣<br />\n<br />\n圖書館木製的窗<br />\n訓導假裝嚴肅的模樣<br />\n還未有傾訴對象<br />\n仍未覺得悲涼<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n每天在風光的戰場<br />\n騎著馬去到邊疆<br />\n所到之地全是賜賞<br />\n<br />\nHoo 寂靜但不漫長<br />\nHoo 寂靜但不漫長<br />\nHoo 寂靜但不漫長<br />\nHoo 寂靜但不漫長<br />\n<br />\nLa-la-la-la-la<br />\nLa-la-la-la-la<br />\nLa-la-la-la-la (那陣時不知道)<br />\nLa-la-la-la-la<br />\nLa-la-la-la-la"},{"pid":"afaa6b7682916ea41d16df707c42f6b4cdfb5b6e","tid":2406171,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73534048df151ec1a2e63440ba21378cc34a340","tid":2406171,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7118b1778dc24bb998b4e955e6b776bab7d961","tid":2406171,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29f07a495cdc34f33fa0d062836c97eb